## Channel Selection Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define objectives: Brand awareness, consideration, conversion, retention
- [ ] 2. Know the audience: Where does the target audience spend time online/offline?
- [ ] 3. Assess channel fit: Evaluate each channel against audience and objectives
- [ ] 4. Consider budget: Match channel ambitions to realistic budget
- [ ] 5. Build the mix: Select primary, secondary, and supporting channels
- [ ] 6. Plan attribution: How will performance be tracked across channels?
- [ ] 7. Document rationale: Explain why each channel was chosen or rejected

## Key Inputs
- Target audience: {{target_audience}}
- Campaign objectives: {{objectives}}
- Budget: {{budget}}
- Time period: {{time_period}}
- Available channels: {{available_channels}}
